  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a developmental project with two phases. The first phase will adapt an existing
      web-based intervention to incorporate mind-body exercises to develop a multi-modal
      intervention to promote physical activity in patients with COPD and HF. The second phase will
      pilot test this new intervention in a longitudinal study (subjects randomized to intervention
      or usual care).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
